OL,3,CCurve head of finance jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing 'breath-taking' sum from
OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,FThe former head of finance at the
OL,8,FCurve theatre has been jailed for four
OL,9,Fyears and 10 months for stealing more
OL,10,Fthan #868,800 from the theatre, which
OL,11,Fis a registered charity.
OL,13,FAfter her arrest, Karen McGowan, 50,
OL,14,Fblamed colleagues who worked alongside
OL,15,Fher for taking the money and also
OL,16,Fsuggested a "dark web attack" on the
OL,17,Ftheatre could be responsible.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
