OL,3,CCurve head of finance jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing 'breath-taking' sum from
OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,FBut really she had simply been sending
OL,8,Fmoney - in sums of up to about #28,000
OL,9,F- into her 57-year-old husband Graham
OL,10,FMcGowan's bank account.
OL,12,FMost of the money was gambled away and
OL,13,Fused to pay Karen McGowan's gambling
OL,14,Fdebts.JShe and her husband, both of
OL,15,FHarlequin Road, Sileby, near
OL,16,FLoughborough, appeared at Leicester
OL,17,FCrown Court on Friday.
OL,19,FHer husband was given a 23-month
OL,20,Fsentence suspended for two years.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/18
