OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,FThose in the public gallery at the
OL,8,Fhearing included the theatre's chief
OL,9,Fexecutive Chris Stafford and a female
OL,10,Fmember of the finance team who had
OL,11,Fbeen questioned under caution after
OL,12,FKaren McGowan redirected the blame
OL,13,Ftowards her.
OL,15,FMr Stafford read out a statement from
OL,16,Fthe witness box about the shock and
OL,17,Fsadness, as well as the financial
OL,18,Fimpact, caused by the couple's actions.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
