OL,3,CCurve head of finance jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing 'breath-taking' sum from
OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,FHe said: "Members of the team - good,
OL,8,Fhonest people - had to be interviewed
OL,9,Fby the police.
OL,11,F"Karen raised a number of false claims
OL,12,Fabout how the fraud might have
OL,13,Fhappened, including as part of a dark
OL,14,Fweb attack on the Curve's system."
OL,16,FHe said staff were breaking down in
OL,17,Ftears in his office after the news
OL,18,Femerged Karen McGowan had been charged.
OL,20,FHe added: "Karen was only ever treated
OL,21,Fwith kindness and respect.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/18
