OL,4,Cstealing 'breath-taking' sum from
OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,F"Karen knew exactly what she was doing
OL,8,Fand would have known the impact her
OL,9,Factions would have on the theatre, our
OL,10,Ffinances and the people she worked
OL,11,Fwith on a daily basis."
OL,13,FHe said his staff were also very upset
OL,14,Fat being witnesses in the trial.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/18
