OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,FThe first trial was due to happen in
OL,8,FJune 2021 but there were numerous
OL,9,Fdelays due to the post-Covid backlog
OL,10,Fin the court system, leading to
OL,11,Ffurther trial dates in January 2022,
OL,12,FNovember 2022 and March 2023 that
OL,13,Fnever happened.
OL,15,FTwo weeks before the March 2023 trial
OL,16,Fdate, Karen McGowan changed her pleas
OL,17,Fto guilty.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/18
