OL,3,CCurve head of finance jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing 'breath-taking' sum from
OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,FGraham McGowan only pleaded guilty on
OL,8,Fthe second day of his trial, which
OL,9,Fbegan on Monday (September 23) at
OL,10,FLeicester Crown Court.
OL,12,FKaren McGowan had pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Ftwo counts of fraud by abuse of
OL,14,Fposition and one of money laundering
OL,15,Fand her husband admitted to one charge
OL,16,Fof money laundering.
OL,18,FProsecutor Andrew Peet told the court
OL,19,Fthe delays were entirely the couple's
OL,20,Ffault for failing to admit their guilt
OL,21,Fearlier.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/18
