OL,7,FHe said: "The delay has been caused
OL,8,Fentirely by the defendants - putting
OL,9,Ftheir heads in the sand or denying the
OL,10,Fcharges outright."
OL,12,FThe court heard Karen McGowan got a
OL,13,Fjob at the Curve finance department in
OL,14,FOctober 2014, covering for a woman on
OL,15,Fmaternity leave.
OL,17,FShe got a permanent job the following
OL,18,Fyear, earning #26,000 and was promoted
OL,19,Fto finance manager in October 2015,
OL,20,Fearning #30,000.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/18
