OL,7,FIn February 2019, she was made head of
OL,8,Ffinance on a salary of #34,340. Her
OL,9,Ffraud was uncovered two months after
OL,10,Fthat promotion.
OL,12,FThe theatre was alerted to the fraud
OL,13,Fby Graham McGowan's bank.
OL,15,FThe joint investigation by the bank
OL,16,Fand the theatre discovered the 104
OL,17,Ftransactions from the Curve bank
OL,18,Faccount to Graham McGowan's account
OL,19,Fover 17 months.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/18
