OL,4,Cstealing 'breath-taking' sum from
OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,FIn total, #868,804 was taken. The
OL,8,Faccounts showed increasing amounts
OL,9,Fbeing taken over time, with more than
OL,10,F#140,000 being taken "in a matter of
OL,11,Fdays" at the height of the fraud, Mr
OL,12,FPeet said.
OL,14,FHe added: "There are increases in
OL,15,Ffrequency and increases in amounts
OL,16,Fbecause they don't get caught." The
OL,17,Fbiggest single transfer was #28,454.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/18
