OL,7,FMr Peet described how Karen McGowan
OL,8,Fstayed for long hours at work each day
OL,9,Fand never took holidays to ensure she
OL,10,Fcould "keep a lid on things" and avoid
OL,11,Fanyone else looking closely into the
OL,12,Faccounts.
OL,14,FHe said she was a "micro-manager" who
OL,15,Fwas "unwilling to delegate" and
OL,16,F"controlled the department to prevent
OL,17,Fdiscovery of her dishonesty".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/18
