OL,4,Cstealing 'breath-taking' sum from
OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,FHe added: "The Curve is a charity. It
OL,8,Fexists on the goodwill of the public
OL,9,Fand the provision of public funds via
OL,10,Fthe charity commission.
OL,12,F"She held a largely-unchecked position
OL,13,Fof trust within the charity."
OL,15,FSaleema Mahmood, representing Karen
OL,16,FMcGowan, told the court her client
OL,17,Fstarted gambling - at first with
OL,18,Fscratch cards - to help make money at
OL,19,Fa point the couple were in a "dire"
OL,20,Ffinancial situation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/18
