OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,FJohn Lucas, representing Graham
OL,8,FMcGowan, said his client was
OL,9,F"pathetic" and "under his wife's
OL,10,Fcontrol".
OL,12,FHe added the couple met in the
OL,13,FTerritorial Army and his client had
OL,14,Fworked for BT as an engineer for 27
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FMr Lucas continued: "This is a case of
OL,18,Fbecoming compliant in something he did
OL,19,Fnot instigate.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/18
