OL,3,CCurve head of finance jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing 'breath-taking' sum from
OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,F"Mr McGowan did not steal any money,
OL,8,Fhe did not gamble any money. He had a
OL,9,Fhumble lifestyle. He let it happen -
OL,10,Fhe trusted her.
OL,12,F"He turned a blind eye to it because
OL,13,Fhe loved his wife. Not a shred of that
OL,14,Fmoney affected him in terms of the
OL,15,Fquality of his life - that's why it's
OL,16,Fan extremely sad case."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/18
