OL,7,FDuring Mr Lucas's speech, Karen
OL,8,FMcGowan began having a medical episode
OL,9,Fin the dock and her husband, sat
OL,10,Fbeside her, was trying to help her
OL,11,Fcontrol her breathing.
OL,13,FAfter lunch, Ms Mahmood told Judge
OL,14,FTimothy Spencer KC: "There were
OL,15,Fconcerns regarding the symptoms Mrs
OL,16,FMcGowan was exhibiting and she was
OL,17,Ftaken to hospital.
OL,19,F"I asked if she wanted to be present
OL,20,Ffor sentence being passed and she said
OL,21,Fshe did not."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/18
