OL,7,FThe judge agreed to sentence her in
OL,8,Fher absence, adding later that he
OL,9,Fbelieved her "panic attack" was
OL,10,Fgenuine and "probably prompted by the
OL,11,Fdeep shame" she felt having Mr
OL,12,FStafford and other members of the
OL,13,FCurve team attending the sentencing
OL,14,Fhearing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/18
