OL,3,CCurve head of finance jailed for
OL,4,Cstealing 'breath-taking' sum from
OL,5,Ctheatre
OL,7,FPassing his sentencing remarks, Judge
OL,8,FSpencer said Karen McGowan had caused
OL,9,F"huge damage" to the people who worked
OL,10,Fwith her as well as stealing an "eye-
OL,11,Fwatering" amount of money from a
OL,12,Ftheatre that existed as a charity
OL,13,Frelying on its reputation.
OL,15,FCommenting on the fraud, he added:
OL,16,F"The modus operandi was relatively
OL,17,Fsimple - not overly sophisticated and
OL,18,Fprobably bound to be discovered."
OL,20,FA proceeds of crime hearing is
OL,21,Fscheduled for March next year.
